				</header>
				
				<p>HAMR was awarded a Harvard Integrated Life Sciences grant to host an interdisciplinary symposium on antimicrobial resistance. We heard fantastic talks from trainees and faculty working on areas ranging from drug development to population-wide epidemiology. Thanks to all the speakers and attendees for a successful event!</p>
